        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】小米發佈 15 Ultra 國際版，支援 iPhone 互傳相 / 片 + 同場發佈 15 + 開售詳情公佈</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/mi15ultra-intl-version-launched-hk-price-revealed/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mi15ultra-intl-version-launched-hk-price-revealed</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/mi15ultra-intl-version-launched-hk-price-revealed/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 04:02:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[15 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[leica]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米 15 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294971</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米在香港時間中午 12 時就在西班牙巴塞隆那的 MWC 大會前夕，發佈了新一代的真。旗艦拍攝手機 15 Ultra 的國際版，亦同場宣佈會推出國際版的小米 15，現場亦公佈了香港的開售詳情，想知更多就要瀏覽 Edward 的現場報導了。</p><h2>15 Ultra 國行發佈一星期旋即推國際版</h2><p>首先最引人注目的，肯定是小米在推出 15 Ultra 國行版本數天後，旋即推出該機的國際版。它在外形上繼承了一部分上代小米 14 Ultra 的特點，機背黑、白色採用了航天級玻璃纖維作機背，而最特別的黑銀色更結合了航天級玻璃纖維及 PU 皮革作機揹物料，十分有 LEICA 相機的設計風格。另外，機身亦採用了升級版的 Xiaomi Guardian 架構，耐跌表現比以往採用 Xiaomi Shield Glass 2.0 的機款提升了 16 倍，而框架亦採用了高強度電腦加工製的鋁金屬物料，令機身保持輕巧之餘亦不失高耐用度。鏡頭亦同樣採用了 Corning Gorilla Glass 7i 強化玻璃保護，有效提升抗摔防刮等效果。加上機身支援 IP68 防水防塵功能，令使用上亦更安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09979-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09979-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09979.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是小米最新推出的 15 Ultra 國際版，大家可以見到從正面看，與上代分別不算很大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09952-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09952-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09952.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機背採用了航天級玻璃纖維作機背，微磨砂的表面既硬淨亦頗有手感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295081" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155821-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155821-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155821.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至於白色機就在機背加入了曲線花紋，十分優雅漂亮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295082" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155709-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155709-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155709.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155723-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155723-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155723.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不過筆者覺得最有型的依然是這款黑銀兩色版本，設計上更像一部懷舊 LEICA 相機，使用時更有感覺。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09960-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09960-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09960.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲框架採用了高強度電腦加工製的鋁金屬物料，令機身保持輕巧之餘亦不失高耐用度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09965-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09965-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09965.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身亦採用了升級版的 Xiaomi Guardian 架構，耐跌表現比以往採用 Xiaomi Shield Glass 2.0 的機款提升了 16 倍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09982-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09982-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09982.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09984-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09984-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09984.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身不算厚及闊，單手握機操控手感算不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294998" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09990-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09990-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09990.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09988-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09988-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09988.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重量方面，小米 15 Ultra 為 229.3g，不算很重。</p><h2>「雙大底」相機遠近拍攝均佳</h2><p>而重點的相機方面，今代採用了「大三元」式全焦段鏡頭配置，主鏡除了延續採用 LEICA Summilux 鏡頭組及 8P 非球面高透光鏡片外，四個主鏡亦覆蓋了由 14mm 超廣角到 200mm 超長焦全焦段，令用家拍攝時更具彈性。當中除了 5,000 萬像素主攝依然採用了「超大底」1 吋感光元件外，超長焦的像素亦提升至 2 億像素，感光元件尺寸亦達到 1/1.4 吋，這種「雙大底」配置令用家無論是使用主攝鏡還是超長焦鏡拍攝，遠近的成像質素，尤其是低光、夜攝場景中也有明顯提升。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295014" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09956-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09956-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09956.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次小米 15 Ultra 依然採用 LEICA Summilux 鏡頭組及 8P 非球面高透光鏡片架構，設有 4 個鏡頭，分別是均是 5,000 萬像素的主攝鏡、超廣角鏡、浮動長焦鏡、以及 2 億像素的潛望長焦鏡。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09959-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09959-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09959.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次的主相機最特別的地方，就是除了主攝鏡依然採用 1 吋感光元件外，潛望長焦鏡的感光元件亦達到 1/1.4 吋，這個「雙大底」配置，理論上可令遠近的成像質素，尤其是低光、夜攝場景中也有明顯提升，不過亦因如此，主相機模組依然有一定厚度及面積。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-1-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-1-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-2-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-2-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大家亦可見到只有超級長焦鏡可以在超高清模式拍到 2 億像素相片，其他鏡頭就只能拍到最高 5,000 萬像素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502241-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502241-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502241.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小米 15 Ultra 介面上有少許改動，副目錄改為用手指一滑拉出，比以往要滑到最盡頭的目錄再選擇更順手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113759-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113759-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113759-scaled.jpg 1040w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113802-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113802-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113802-scaled.jpg 1040w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113807-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113807-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113807-scaled.jpg 1040w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113809-668x580.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113809-668x580.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113809-scaled.jpg 1036w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 668px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這就是在日間以 4 個鏡頭：超廣角（第一張）、主攝（第二張）、浮動長焦（第三張）及潛望長焦（第四張）鏡拍攝的效果，大家可以見到每個鏡頭成像都十分不錯，顏色還原度高之餘亦十分清晰，即使暗位亦能看到一定程度的細節，表現值得一讚。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-607x900.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-scaled.jpg 608w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當中潛望長焦鏡可以有效壓縮取景，令相片主題更集中。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1295040 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-607x900.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-scaled.jpg 608w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1295041 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-607x900.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-scaled.jpg 608w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而使用潛望長焦鏡拍攝人像相片，效果亦十分吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此外，小米 15 Ultra 的遠攝亦加入了 AI 功能提升清晰度，只要點按下方的 AI 按鍵就可以了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144745-668x580.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144745-668x580.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144745-scaled.jpg 1036w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 668px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144749-668x580.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144749-668x580.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144749-scaled.jpg 1036w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 668px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這兩張就是在聖家堂室內，在以潛望長焦鏡及 120x 2791mm 數碼變焦拍攝，分別沒有開啟 AI 清晰化（第一張）及開啟了 AI 清晰化（第二張）兩者的效果，大家很明顯見到 AI 補圖的相片，真的清晰很多，而且與真實情況近乎完全相同，可見 AI 表現十分不錯。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00839-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00839-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00839.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外今次小米的街拍模式，亦十分方便大家快速拍攝相片，如果配合手柄的話會更好玩，下文會再詳述。</p><br /><b>
